data.description: Welcome to this amazing home located in the heart of the Vista Del Sol subdivision. Fully equipped with 4 bedrooms, two full bathrooms, two living areas, primary bedroom located downstairs. Walking distance from Myrtle cooper elementary school. Pertains to Walter Clarke Middle School and Americas High School. Just 25 minutes from Ft. Bliss and WBAMC. Home is being sold 'AS IS', no repairs will be completed. Take advantage of this great investment opportunity. This amazing deal won't last long!
